{"tid":1059131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中國黑人網紅有愛滋　「7個女人已中鏢」","createTime":"2019-03-13T02:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T04:23:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69249827bc91c409554e4713bb48561e02887d6b","tid":1059131,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190312/640_db5d710e3377c6648dc728a5223bacca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190312%2F640_db5d710e3377c6648dc728a5223bacca.jpg&h=8f16ed3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名在中國當網紅的黑人，被爆料有愛滋病病毒（HIV)，跟他啪啪啪過的7個女人中鏢。<br />\n網友「莫問奴歸處v」在《微博》發文指出，有網友爆料指出，網紅黑人主播「司馬缸」是位有HIV傳染病的黑人，在瀋陽已經傳染給7個女人，「我相信那些女孩是被騙了，我痛恨這個黑人，希望他滾出中國，不想其他任何地方的女孩再經歷這些」。<br />\n爆料的網友指出，司馬缸從來不戴套，有兩個40多歲的、兩個50、60歲的，還有兩個20、30歲的，還有一個韓國女人，共7個中標。看到這爆料的網友紛紛留言「不知道被騙的女人是獵奇心態還是崇洋心態」、「這人噁心死了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190312/640_413a50df5680eb2b861ff4e21c1db336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190312%2F640_413a50df5680eb2b861ff4e21c1db336.jpg&h=a1f3fbff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190312/640_2fa70b2137f44e321e3488f550a0c317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190312%2F640_2fa70b2137f44e321e3488f550a0c317.jpg&h=0586b6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190312/640_cf53144cfbee0e42265d03f1990a267a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190312%2F640_cf53144cfbee0e42265d03f1990a267a.jpg&h=94e04518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190312/1531942/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A